metadata.name: "REVIVE"
metadata.description:
“REVIVE” by Lago

1 of 1 Limited Edition.

This piece was created during a small turning point for me when I was immersed in some difficult circumstances. 

It symbolizes the energy and possibility of reinventing ourselves and rising again from unfavorable situations, and that we are strong to do so if we really desire it. 

First piece minted in my own ERC721 smart contract.
